Output kb.gif

Set Shell "zsh"
Set FontSize 18
Set Width 1200
Set Height 720
Set Padding 20
Set WindowBar Colorful
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set TypingSpeed 50ms
Set PlaybackSpeed 2.0

Type "veles add sources/raft-consensus.md" Enter
Sleep 20s
Type "veles run 'In two sentences, how does Raft elect a leader?'" Enter
Sleep 14s
